Constraint & Skin Utility Tool

Goal: Fast rigging utility for common setup tasks.

Features

Create constraints:
Parent Constraint
Point Constraint
Orient Constraint
Scale Constraint
maintainOffset
Support:
One → One
One → Many
Many → One
Simple UI with:
Source List
Target List
Skin Utilities:
Copy Skin Weights (Mesh A → Mesh B)
Copy Skin 
Bind Skin with selected joints
Optional:
Maintain Offset toggle

Pipeline-Production-Tool/
├── main.py                        # Entry point
├── requirements.txt               # Python dependencies
├── README.md
└── src/
    ├── app.py                     # App init — loads stylesheet, launches Main window
    ├── constants.py               # All app-wide constants (paths, defaults, domain lists)
    ├── Validation.py              # validation to check the type and number of object located
    ├── resources/
    │   └── style.qss              # App-wide stylesheet
    └── ui/
        ├── main_window.py         # Main window 
        ├── Contraint_Tool.py      # constraintTool      
	├── Connection_Tool.py     # ConnectionTool 
        └── Skin_Tool.py           # SkinTool Ui  




